Happy Hoppers
Single-file HTML/CSS/JS kid-friendly hopping game
Controls:
 - Space / Up arrow / Click / Tap to jump
 - Left/Right arrows to move (optional)
Objective: Collect stars, avoid falling. Simple, colorful, responsive.
Designed for quick preview and easy customization.
-->

